var book = {
	"name": "Micah",
	"numChapters": 7,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> that came to Micah of Moresheth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22581A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22581A\"></sup> during the reigns of Jotham,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22581B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22581B\"></sup> Ahaz<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22581C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22581C\"></sup> and Hezekiah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22581D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22581D\"></sup> kings of Judah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22581E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22581E\"></sup>—the vision<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22581F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22581F\"></sup> he saw concerning Samaria and Jerusalem.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Hear,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22582G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22582G\"></sup> you peoples, all of you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22582H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22582H\"></sup>listen, earth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22582I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22582I\"></sup> and all who live in it,that the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> may bear witness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22582J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22582J\"></sup> against you,the Lord from his holy temple.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22582K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22582K\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Look! The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is coming from his dwelling<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22583L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22583L\"></sup> place;he comes down<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22583M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22583M\"></sup> and treads on the heights of the earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22583N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22583N\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The mountains melt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22584O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22584O\"></sup> beneath him<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22584P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22584P\"></sup>and the valleys split apart,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22584Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22584Q\"></sup>like wax before the fire,like water rushing down a slope.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>All this is because of Jacob’s transgression,because of the sins of the people of Israel.What is Jacob’s transgression?Is it not Samaria?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22585R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22585R\"></sup>What is Judah’s high place?Is it not Jerusalem?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Therefore I will make Samaria a heap of rubble,a place for planting vineyards.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22586S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22586S\"></sup>I will pour her stones<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22586T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22586T\"></sup> into the valleyand lay bare her foundations.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22586U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22586U\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>All her idols<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22587V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22587V\"></sup> will be broken to pieces;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22587W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22587W\"></sup>all her temple gifts will be burned with fire;I will destroy all her images.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22587X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22587X\"></sup>Since she gathered her gifts from the wages of prostitutes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22587Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22587Y\"></sup>as the wages of prostitutes they will again be used.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Because of this I will weep<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22588Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22588Z\"></sup> and wail;I will go about barefoot<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22588AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22588AA\"></sup> and naked.I will howl like a jackaland moan like an owl.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For Samaria’s plague<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22589AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22589AB\"></sup> is incurable;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22589AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22589AC\"></sup>it has spread to Judah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22589AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22589AD\"></sup>It has reached the very gate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22589AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22589AE\"></sup> of my people,even to Jerusalem itself.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Tell it not in Gath;weep not at all.In Beth Ophrahroll in the dust.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Pass by naked<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22591AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22591AF\"></sup> and in shame,you who live in Shaphir.Those who live in Zaananwill not come out.Beth Ezel is in mourning;it no longer protects you.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Those who live in Maroth writhe in pain,waiting for relief,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22592AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22592AG\"></sup>because disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22592AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22592AH\"></sup> has come from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,even to the gate of Jerusalem.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>You who live in Lachish,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22593AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22593AI\"></sup>harness fast horses to the chariot.You are where the sin of Daughter Zion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22593AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22593AJ\"></sup> began,for the transgressions of Israel were found in you.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Therefore you will give parting gifts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22594AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22594AK\"></sup>to Moresheth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22594AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22594AL\"></sup> Gath.The town of Akzib<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22594AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22594AM\"></sup> will prove deceptive<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22594AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22594AN\"></sup>to the kings of Israel.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I will bring a conqueror against youwho live in Mareshah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22595AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22595AO\"></sup>The nobles of Israelwill flee to Adullam.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22595AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22595AP\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Shave<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22596AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22596AQ\"></sup> your head in mourningfor the children in whom you delight;make yourself as bald as the vulture,for they will go from you into exile.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22596AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22596AR\"></sup>"
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>Woe to those who plan iniquity,to those who plot evil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22597A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22597A\"></sup> on their beds!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22597B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22597B\"></sup>At morning’s light they carry it outbecause it is in their power to do it.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>They covet fields<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22598C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22598C\"></sup> and seize them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22598D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22598D\"></sup>and houses, and take them.They defraud<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22598E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22598E\"></sup> people of their homes,they rob them of their inheritance.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22598F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22598F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Therefore, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“I am planning disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22599G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22599G\"></sup> against this people,from which you cannot save yourselves.You will no longer walk proudly,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22599H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22599H\"></sup>for it will be a time of calamity.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>In that day people will ridicule you;they will taunt you with this mournful song:‘We are utterly ruined;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22600I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22600I\"></sup>my people’s possession is divided up.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22600J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22600J\"></sup>He takes it from me!He assigns our fields to traitors.’”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Therefore you will have no one in the assembly of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>to divide the land<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22601K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22601K\"></sup> by lot.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22601L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22601L\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Do not prophesy,” their prophets say.“Do not prophesy about these things;disgrace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22602M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22602M\"></sup> will not overtake us.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22602N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22602N\"></sup>”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>You descendants of Jacob, should it be said,“Does the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> become impatient?Does he do such things?”“Do not my words do good<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22603O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22603O\"></sup>to the one whose ways are upright?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22603P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22603P\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Lately my people have risen uplike an enemy.You strip off the rich robefrom those who pass by without a care,like men returning from battle.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>You drive the women of my peoplefrom their pleasant homes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22605Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22605Q\"></sup>You take away my blessingfrom their children forever.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Get up, go away!For this is not your resting place,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22606R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22606R\"></sup>because it is defiled,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22606S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22606S\"></sup>it is ruined, beyond all remedy.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>If a liar and deceiver<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22607T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22607T\"></sup> comes and says,‘I will prophesy for you plenty of wine and beer,’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22607U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22607U\"></sup>that would be just the prophet for this people!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22607V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22607V\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“I will surely gather all of you, Jacob;I will surely bring together the remnant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22608W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22608W\"></sup> of Israel.I will bring them together like sheep in a pen,like a flock in its pasture;the place will throng with people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22608X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22608X\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The One who breaks open the way will go up before<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22609Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22609Y\"></sup> them;they will break through the gate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22609Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22609Z\"></sup> and go out.Their King will pass through before them,the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> at their head.”"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>Then I said,“Listen, you leaders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22610A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22610A\"></sup> of Jacob,you rulers of Israel.Should you not embrace justice,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>you who hate good and love evil;who tear the skin from my peopleand the flesh from their bones;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22611B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22611B\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>who eat my people’s flesh,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22612C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22612C\"></sup>strip off their skinand break their bones in pieces;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22612D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22612D\"></sup>who chop<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22612E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22612E\"></sup> them up like meat for the pan,like flesh for the pot?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22612F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22612F\"></sup>”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then they will cry out to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,but he will not answer them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22613G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22613G\"></sup>At that time he will hide his face<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22613H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22613H\"></sup> from thembecause of the evil they have done.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22613I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22613I\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“As for the prophetswho lead my people astray,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22614J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22614J\"></sup>they proclaim ‘peace’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22614K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22614K\"></sup>if they have something to eat,but prepare to wage war against anyonewho refuses to feed them.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Therefore night will come over you, without visions,and darkness, without divination.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22615L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22615L\"></sup>The sun will set for the prophets,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22615M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22615M\"></sup>and the day will go dark for them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22615N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22615N\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The seers will be ashamed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22616O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22616O\"></sup>and the diviners disgraced.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22616P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22616P\"></sup>They will all cover<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22616Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22616Q\"></sup> their faces<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22616R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22616R\"></sup>because there is no answer from God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22616S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22616S\"></sup>”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But as for me, I am filled with power,with the Spirit of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and with justice and might,to declare to Jacob his transgression,to Israel his sin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22617T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22617T\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Hear this, you leaders of Jacob,you rulers of Israel,who despise justiceand distort all that is right;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22618U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22618U\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>who build<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22619V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22619V\"></sup> Zion with bloodshed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22619W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22619W\"></sup>and Jerusalem with wickedness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22619X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22619X\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Her leaders judge for a bribe,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22620Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22620Y\"></sup>her priests teach for a price,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22620Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22620Z\"></sup>and her prophets tell fortunes for money.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22620AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22620AA\"></sup>Yet they look<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22620AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22620AB\"></sup> for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s support and say,“Is not the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> among us?No disaster will come upon us.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22620AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22620AC\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Therefore because of you,Zion will be plowed like a field,Jerusalem will become a heap of rubble,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22621AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22621AD\"></sup>the temple<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22621AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22621AE\"></sup> hill a mound overgrown with thickets.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22621AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22621AF\"></sup>"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>In the last daysthe mountain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22622B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22622B\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s temple will be establishedas the highest of the mountains;it will be exalted above the hills,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22622C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22622C\"></sup>and peoples will stream to it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22622D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22622D\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Many nations will come and say,“Come, let us go up to the mountain of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22623E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22623E\"></sup>to the temple of the God of Jacob.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22623F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22623F\"></sup>He will teach us<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22623G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22623G\"></sup> his ways,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22623H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22623H\"></sup>so that we may walk in his paths.”The law<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22623I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22623I\"></sup> will go out from Zion,the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> from Jerusalem.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>He will judge between many peoplesand will settle disputes for strong nations far and wide.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22624J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22624J\"></sup>They will beat their swords into plowsharesand their spears into pruning hooks.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22624K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22624K\"></sup>Nation will not take up sword against nation,nor will they train for war<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22624L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22624L\"></sup> anymore.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22624M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22624M\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Everyone will sit under their own vineand under their own fig tree,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22625N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22625N\"></sup>and no one will make them afraid,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22625O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22625O\"></sup>for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty has spoken.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22625P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22625P\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>All the nations may walkin the name of their gods,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22626Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22626Q\"></sup>but we will walk in the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>our God for ever and ever.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22626R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22626R\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“In that day,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“I will gather the lame;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22627S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22627S\"></sup>I will assemble the exiles<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22627T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22627T\"></sup>and those I have brought to grief.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22627U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22627U\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I will make the lame my remnant,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22628V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22628V\"></sup>those driven away a strong nation.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22628W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22628W\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will rule over them in Mount Zion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22628X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22628X\"></sup>from that day and forever.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22628Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22628Y\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>As for you, watchtower of the flock,stronghold of Daughter Zion,the former dominion will be restored<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22629Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22629Z\"></sup> to you;kingship will come to Daughter Jerusalem.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22629AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22629AA\"></sup>”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Why do you now cry aloud—have you no king<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22630AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22630AB\"></sup>?Has your ruler perished,that pain seizes you like that of a woman in labor?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22630AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22630AC\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Writhe in agony, Daughter Zion,like a woman in labor,for now you must leave the cityto camp in the open field.You will go to Babylon;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22631AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22631AD\"></sup>there you will be rescued.There the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will redeem<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22631AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22631AE\"></sup> youout of the hand of your enemies.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But now many nationsare gathered against you.They say, “Let her be defiled,let our eyes gloat<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22632AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22632AF\"></sup> over Zion!”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But they do not knowthe thoughts of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;they do not understand his plan,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22633AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22633AG\"></sup>that he has gathered them like sheaves to the threshing floor.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Rise and thresh,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22634AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22634AH\"></sup> Daughter Zion,for I will give you horns of iron;I will give you hooves of bronze,and you will break to pieces many nations.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22634AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22634AI\"></sup>You will devote their ill-gotten gains to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22634AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22634AJ\"></sup>their wealth to the Lord of all the earth."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>Marshal your troops now, city of troops,for a siege is laid against us.They will strike Israel’s ruleron the cheek<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22635A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22635A\"></sup> with a rod.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“But you, Bethlehem<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22636B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22636B\"></sup> Ephrathah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22636C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22636C\"></sup>though you are small among the clans of Judah,out of you will come for meone who will be ruler<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22636D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22636D\"></sup> over Israel,whose origins are from of old,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22636E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22636E\"></sup>from ancient times.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22636F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22636F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Therefore Israel will be abandoned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22637G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22637G\"></sup>until the time when she who is in labor bears a son,and the rest of his brothers returnto join the Israelites.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>He will stand and shepherd his flock<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22638H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22638H\"></sup>in the strength of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,in the majesty of the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> his God.And they will live securely, for then his greatness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22638I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22638I\"></sup>will reach to the ends of the earth.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And he will be our peace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22639J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22639J\"></sup>when the Assyrians invade<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22639K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22639K\"></sup> our landand march through our fortresses.We will raise against them seven shepherds,even eight commanders,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22639L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22639L\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>who will rule the land of Assyria with the sword,the land of Nimrod<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22640M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22640M\"></sup> with drawn sword.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22640N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22640N\"></sup>He will deliver us from the Assyrianswhen they invade our landand march across our borders.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22640O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22640O\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The remnant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22641P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22641P\"></sup> of Jacob will bein the midst of many peopleslike dew<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22641Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22641Q\"></sup> from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,like showers on the grass,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22641R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22641R\"></sup>which do not wait for anyoneor depend on man.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The remnant of Jacob will be among the nations,in the midst of many peoples,like a lion among the beasts of the forest,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22642S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22642S\"></sup>like a young lion among flocks of sheep,which mauls and mangles<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22642T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22642T\"></sup> as it goes,and no one can rescue.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22642U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22642U\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Your hand will be lifted up<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22643V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22643V\"></sup> in triumph over your enemies,and all your foes will be destroyed.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“In that day,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“I will destroy your horses from among youand demolish your chariots.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22644W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22644W\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I will destroy the cities<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22645X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22645X\"></sup> of your landand tear down all your strongholds.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22645Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22645Y\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I will destroy your witchcraftand you will no longer cast spells.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22646Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22646Z\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I will destroy your idols<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22647AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22647AA\"></sup>and your sacred stones from among you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22647AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22647AB\"></sup>you will no longer bow downto the work of your hands.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22647AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22647AC\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I will uproot from among you your Asherah poles<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22648AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22648AD\"></sup>when I demolish your cities.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I will take vengeance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22649AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22649AE\"></sup> in anger and wrathon the nations that have not obeyed me.”"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>Listen to what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“Stand up, plead my case before the mountains;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22650A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22650A\"></sup>let the hills hear what you have to say.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Hear,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22651B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22651B\"></sup> you mountains, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s accusation;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22651C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22651C\"></sup>listen, you everlasting foundations of the earth.For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has a case<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22651D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22651D\"></sup> against his people;he is lodging a charge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22651E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22651E\"></sup> against Israel.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“My people, what have I done to you?How have I burdened<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22652F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22652F\"></sup> you?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22652G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22652G\"></sup> Answer me.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I brought you up out of Egypt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22653H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22653H\"></sup>and redeemed you from the land of slavery.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22653I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22653I\"></sup>I sent Moses<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22653J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22653J\"></sup> to lead you,also Aaron<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22653K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22653K\"></sup> and Miriam.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22653L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22653L\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>My people, rememberwhat Balak<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22654M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22654M\"></sup> king of Moab plottedand what Balaam son of Beor answered.Remember your journey from Shittim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22654N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22654N\"></sup> to Gilgal,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22654O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22654O\"></sup>that you may know the righteous acts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22654P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22654P\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>With what shall I come before<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22655Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22655Q\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>and bow down before the exalted God?Shall I come before him with burnt offerings,with calves a year old?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22655R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22655R\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Will the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> be pleased with thousands of rams,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22656S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22656S\"></sup>with ten thousand rivers of olive oil?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22656T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22656T\"></sup>Shall I offer my firstborn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22656U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22656U\"></sup> for my transgression,the fruit of my body for the sin of my soul?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22656V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22656V\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He has shown you, O mortal, what is good.And what does the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> require of you?To act justly<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22657W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22657W\"></sup> and to love mercyand to walk humbly<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22657X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22657X\"></sup> with your God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22657Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22657Y\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Listen! The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is calling to the city—and to fear your name is wisdom—“Heed the rod<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22658Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22658Z\"></sup> and the One who appointed it.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Am I still to forget your ill-gotten treasures, you wicked house,and the short ephah, which is accursed?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22659AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22659AA\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Shall I acquit someone with dishonest scales,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22660AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22660AB\"></sup>with a bag of false weights?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22660AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22660AC\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Your rich people are violent;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22661AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22661AD\"></sup>your inhabitants are liars<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22661AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22661AE\"></sup>and their tongues speak deceitfully.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22661AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22661AF\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Therefore, I have begun to destroy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22662AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22662AG\"></sup> you,to ruin you because of your sins.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>You will eat but not be satisfied;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22663AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22663AH\"></sup>your stomach will still be empty.You will store up but save nothing,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22663AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22663AI\"></sup>because what you save I will give to the sword.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>You will plant but not harvest;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22664AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22664AJ\"></sup>you will press olives but not use the oil,you will crush grapes but not drink the wine.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22664AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22664AK\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>You have observed the statutes of Omri<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22665AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22665AL\"></sup>and all the practices of Ahab’s<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22665AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22665AM\"></sup> house;you have followed their traditions.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22665AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22665AN\"></sup>Therefore I will give you over to ruin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22665AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22665AO\"></sup>and your people to derision;you will bear the scorn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22665AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22665AP\"></sup> of the nations.”"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>What misery is mine!I am like one who gathers summer fruitat the gleaning of the vineyard;there is no cluster of grapes to eat,none of the early figs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22666A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22666A\"></sup> that I crave.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The faithful have been swept from the land;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22667B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22667B\"></sup>not one<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22667C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22667C\"></sup> upright person remains.Everyone lies in wait<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22667D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22667D\"></sup> to shed blood;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22667E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22667E\"></sup>they hunt each other<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22667F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22667F\"></sup> with nets.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22667G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22667G\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Both hands are skilled in doing evil;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22668H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22668H\"></sup>the ruler demands gifts,the judge accepts bribes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22668I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22668I\"></sup>the powerful dictate what they desire—they all conspire together.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The best of them is like a brier,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22669J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22669J\"></sup>the most upright worse than a thorn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22669K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22669K\"></sup> hedge.The day God visits you has come,the day your watchmen sound the alarm.Now is the time of your confusion.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22669L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22669L\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Do not trust a neighbor;put no confidence in a friend.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22670M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22670M\"></sup>Even with the woman who lies in your embraceguard the words of your lips.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For a son dishonors his father,a daughter rises up against her mother,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22671N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22671N\"></sup>a daughter-in-law against her mother-in-law—a man’s enemies are the members of his own household.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22671O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22671O\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But as for me, I watch<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22672P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22672P\"></sup> in hope<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22672Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22672Q\"></sup> for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,I wait for God my Savior;my God will hear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22672R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22672R\"></sup> me.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Do not gloat over me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22673S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22673S\"></sup> my enemy!Though I have fallen, I will rise.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22673T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22673T\"></sup>Though I sit in darkness,the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will be my light.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22673U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22673U\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Because I have sinned against him,I will bear the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s wrath,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22674V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22674V\"></sup>until he pleads my case<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22674W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22674W\"></sup>and upholds my cause.He will bring me out into the light;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22674X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22674X\"></sup>I will see his righteousness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22674Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22674Y\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then my enemy will see itand will be covered with shame,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22675Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22675Z\"></sup>she who said to me,“Where is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22675AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22675AA\"></sup>My eyes will see her downfall;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22675AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22675AB\"></sup>even now she will be trampled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22675AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22675AC\"></sup> underfootlike mire in the streets.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The day for building your walls<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22676AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22676AD\"></sup> will come,the day for extending your boundaries.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>In that day people will come to youfrom Assyria<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22677AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22677AE\"></sup> and the cities of Egypt,even from Egypt to the Euphratesand from sea to seaand from mountain to mountain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22677AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22677AF\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The earth will become desolate because of its inhabitants,as the result of their deeds.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22678AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22678AG\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Shepherd<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22679AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22679AH\"></sup> your people with your staff,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22679AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22679AI\"></sup>the flock of your inheritance,which lives by itself in a forest,in fertile pasturelands.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22679AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22679AJ\"></sup>Let them feed in Bashan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22679AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22679AK\"></sup> and Gilead<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22679AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22679AL\"></sup>as in days long ago.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22679AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22679AM\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“As in the days when you came out of Egypt,I will show them my wonders.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22680AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22680AN\"></sup>”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Nations will see and be ashamed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22681AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22681AO\"></sup>deprived of all their power.They will put their hands over their mouths<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22681AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22681AP\"></sup>and their ears will become deaf.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>They will lick dust<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22682AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22682AQ\"></sup> like a snake,like creatures that crawl on the ground.They will come trembling<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22682AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22682AR\"></sup> out of their dens;they will turn in fear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22682AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22682AS\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our Godand will be afraid of you.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Who is a God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22683AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22683AT\"></sup> like you,who pardons sin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22683AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22683AU\"></sup> and forgives<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22683AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22683AV\"></sup> the transgressionof the remnant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22683AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22683AW\"></sup> of his inheritance?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22683AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22683AX\"></sup>You do not stay angry<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22683AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22683AY\"></sup> foreverbut delight to show mercy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22683AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22683AZ\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>You will again have compassion on us;you will tread our sins underfootand hurl all our iniquities<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22684BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22684BA\"></sup> into the depths of the sea.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22684BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22684BB\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>You will be faithful to Jacob,and show love to Abraham,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22685BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22685BC\"></sup>as you pledged on oath to our ancestors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22685BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22685BD\"></sup>in days long ago.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22685BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22685BE\"></sup>"
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;